sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTP as caikit Runtime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    participant GRPC as caikit Runtime<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local Module)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(Remote Module)
    participant EmbMod as EmbeddingModule
    participant PeftPT as PeftPromptTuning
    participant PeftTGIS as PeftPromptTuningTGIS
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(in-memory GPU/CPU)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformer<br/>(in-memory)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Disk as Local Disk<br/>(prompt vectors)

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference
    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>TextGen: In-process Python call
    TextGen->>HFModel: PyTorch inference<br/>(in-memory)
    HFModel-->>TextGen: Generated text
    TextGen-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 2: TGIS Remote Text Generation
    Client->>GRPC: gRPC NlpService.TextGeneration<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    GRPC->>TextGenTGIS: In-process Python call
    TextGenTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC generation request<br/>TLS (optional) / mTLS (optional)
    TGIS-->>TextGenTGIS: Generated text (streaming)
    TextGenTGIS-->>GRPC: Response stream
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC stream response

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 3: Text Embedding
    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>EmbMod: In-process Python call
    EmbMod->>STModel: SentenceTransformer.encode()<br/>(thread-safe tokenization)
    STModel-->>EmbMod: Embedding vector(s)
    EmbMod-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON embedding response

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 4: Prompt Tuning Training
    Client->>HTTP: POST train API<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>PeftPT: PeftPromptTuning.train()
    PeftPT->>HFModel: PEFT training<br/>(Accelerate mixed-precision)
    HFModel-->>PeftPT: Trained prompt vectors
    PeftPT->>Disk: Save encoder.pt / decoder.pt
    PeftPT-->>HTTP: Training complete
    HTTP-->>Client: Training result

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 5: TGIS Prompt Tuning Inference
    Client->>GRPC: gRPC inference request<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    GRPC->>PeftTGIS: In-process Python call
    PeftTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC with prompt cache<br/>TLS (optional) / mTLS (optional)
    TGIS-->>PeftTGIS: Inference result
    PeftTGIS-->>GRPC: Response
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,Disk: Model Download (optional)
    TextGen->>HFHub: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Token auth (optional)
    HFHub-->>TextGen: Model artifacts
